{"tid":1729812,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"日本瘋傳「普通男」7大條件　網哀：原來我連普通都稱不上","createTime":"2019-11-17T11:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T01:40:06.000Z","uid":32511,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"090d1fc7ccff8d731787e9e035331b081e04a126","tid":1729812,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UBxdQq6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUBxdQq6.jpg&h=1b204762&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次聊起約會對象的條件時，總有不少女生表示自己要求不高，「普普通通就可以了」，但究竟怎樣才算是「普通」呢？近日Twitter瘋傳一張電視節目截圖，列出「普通男」7項必備條件，快來看看你夠不夠資格吧！<br />\n<br />\n「普通男」7大條件：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HNxmx0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HNxmx0.jpg&h=6efad882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHTpcEM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHTpcEM.jpg&h=675c0add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter近日瘋傳一張電視節目截圖，列出「普通男」7項必備條件，大家才明白，原來在女生口中普普通通的男生，其實一點也不普通！<br />\n <br />\n該圖片一度在Twitter瘋傳，引起廣大網民熱議，不少人大喊難度超高，滿足以上條件的根本完全不普通，有人表示「年賺500~600萬日元的30歲單身男性只有日本總人口的6.2%，還未扣掉170cm以下、長子之類的，普通男的稀有度就跟寶可夢的神獸一樣。」<br />\n <br />\n大家覺得以上條件算是普通嗎？不妨留言分享意見吧！"},{"pid":"198a8e7220fa36b6a88f4402ebdc8ebbd5c29585","tid":1729812,"uid":771,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:12:05.000Z","msg":"合格，但都係垃圾一件"},{"pid":"f6e72684c249dcbb0c5563e12bf4650a12e14142","tid":1729812,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"7中4，連普通都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b1517809494f5e42188236e09e4b15011889bf6","tid":1729812,"uid":18279,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:13:40.000Z","msg":"全部連登仔都普通以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16bf68db9d56865f821d075c231692c3c4086a81","tid":1729